{"tid":1779212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「禁起底令」保護範圍擴展至特務警察並涵蓋家屬","createTime":"2019-12-11T13:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T15:53:42.000Z","uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"450d1ceecddbaa312ef5b3e323d8b56da4009dda","tid":1779212,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:44:56.000Z","msg":"「禁起底令」保護範圍擴展至特務警察並涵蓋家屬<br />\n<br />\n高等法院在10月25日頒發「針對警員及其家屬被起底及滋擾」的臨時禁制令，今日宣布修訂禁制令，將保護範圍擴展到特務警察。有關禁制令禁制任何人非法地及故意地，在沒有相關人士的同意下及同時有意圖或相當可能會恐嚇、騷擾、威脅或煩擾相關人士的情況下使用、發佈、傳達或披露給他人屬於警務人員、特務警察、其配偶及或其家庭成員，包括父母、子女或兄弟姊妹的個人資料。禁制令亦禁止協助、造成、慫使、促致、唆使、煽動、協助、教唆或授權他人從事上述任何行為或參與上述任何行為。<br />\n<br />\n2019-12-11 21:31:17 RTHK"},{"pid":"457583a9f581db2bee9278c030fdba417c66655d","tid":1779212,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"香港人幾時先接受司法制度只係一個笑話？班人嘅罪行唔會低過黑警"},{"pid":"f0ad28db45c9efb7c0f66837553125ab02cd2499","tid":1779212,"uid":65449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a4c2f12dd9e9ff733275cb38100d0abb91b29d","tid":1779212,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"司法系統係好被動㗎，好中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家立法都撈埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8ea7ed2f32825d38ae78896b2fea80c7ac6e65","tid":1779212,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:50:17.000Z","msg":"有鳩用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你執行到先講啦"},{"pid":"052323ae0858e924ad35e52415f0b4822d5e1de9","tid":1779212,"uid":297045,"like":0,